Class Summary

PSContentTypeSummary This object represents a single content type summary.
PSContentTypeSummaryChild This object represents a single content type summary child.
PSFieldDescription This object represents a single field description.
PSItemStatus This object represents a single item status at the time it was prepared for edit.
PSItemSummary Represents a content object which is currently an item or folder.
PSKeyword This object represents a single keyword.
PSKeywordChoice This object represents a single keyword choice.
PSRevisions Represent the revision history of an item
PSSearchSummary Extends the PSItemSummary with additional search result fields.
